INSERT INTO k8s_posts VALUES ('347', '1', '2018-12-13 17:00:01', '2018-12-13 09:00:01', '1.打开钉钉windows 客户端，点击头像下拉菜单--&gt;机器人管理--&gt;点击自定义\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-327\" src=\"http://www.yunfuzg.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/dingding1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"676\" height=\"545\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-332\" src=\"http://www.yunfuzg.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/dingding3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"676\" height=\"545\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-333\" src=\"http://www.yunfuzg.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/dingding4.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"676\" height=\"545\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n2.获取钉钉机器人的webhook，点击机器人的管理按钮--&gt;webhook一栏就是需要的信息\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-337\" src=\"http://www.yunfuzg.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/dingding5.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"676\" height=\"545\" />\r\n\r\n3.在zabbix服务端，修改zabbix_server.conf文件中的AlertScriptsPath=/usr/lib/zabbix/alertscripts（把路径指向脚本存放的路径）\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">4.在/usr/lib/zabbix/alertscripts下新建dingding.py文件，文件内容如下：</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">#!/usr/bin/python\r\n# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-\r\n# Author: xxxxxxxx\r\nimport requests\r\nimport json\r\nimport sys\r\nimport os</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">headers = {\'Content-Type\': \'application/json;charset=utf-8\'}\r\napi_url = \"https://oapi.dingtalk.com/robot/send?access_token=88da9ed421bf34a2e0c0cbed6a0f60cd2660d1efb547028f13257b4a5519bb25\"    #api_url修改成你刚刚创建的钉钉webhook</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">def msg(text):\r\njson_text= {\r\n\"msgtype\": \"text\",\r\n\"at\": {\r\n\"atMobiles\": [\r\n\"zabbix\"\r\n],\r\n\"isAtAll\": False\r\n},\r\n\"text\": {\r\n\"content\": text\r\n}\r\n}\r\nprint requests.post(api_url,json.dumps(json_text),headers=headers).content</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">if __name__ == \'__main__\':\r\ntext = sys.argv[1]\r\nmsg(text)</p>\r\n4.将执行权限授给dingding.py,并测试脚本是否正常运行\r\n<pre>[root@localhost alertscripts]# chmod +x dingding.py \r\n[root@localhost alertscripts]# python dingding.py 123\r\n{\"errmsg\":\"ok\",\"errcode\":0}</pre>\r\n5.如出现以上信息和钉钉接受到信息表示脚本运行成功，可以进行下一步操作\r\n\r\n6.使用web浏览器登陆zabbix，选择管理--&gt;报警媒介类型--&gt;点击创建媒体类型--&gt;根据以下信息填写--&gt;点击更新提交\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-341\" src=\"http://www.yunfuzg.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/zabbix1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1069\" height=\"150\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-342\" src=\"http://www.yunfuzg.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/zabbix2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1057\" height=\"454\" />\r\n\r\n7.点击zabbix web端用户配置报警媒介\r\n\r\n点击管理--&gt;用户--&gt;点击你所使用的用户（我用的是默认管理员账号）\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-345\" src=\"http://www.yunfuzg.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/zabbix5.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1055\" height=\"316\" />\r\n\r\n进入用户界面后点击报警媒介--&gt;添加\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-344\" src=\"http://www.yunfuzg.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/zabbix4.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1058\" height=\"274\" />\r\n\r\n根据之前创建脚本填写信息--&gt;点击更新\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-342\" src=\"http://www.yunfuzg.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/zabbix2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1057\" height=\"454\" />\r\n\r\n最后一步点击更新保存配置\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-346\" src=\"http://www.yunfuzg.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/zabbix6.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1053\" height=\"295\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"></p>', 'zabbix实战应用-zabbix配置钉钉报', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '246-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-12-13 17:00:01', '2018-12-13 09:00:01', '', '246', 'http://www.yunfuzg.com/246-revision-v1/347.html', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
