INSERT INTO k8s_posts VALUES ('373', '1', '2018-12-13 18:08:21', '2018-12-13 10:08:21', '<h3>zabbix众多的报警接收工具中，个人还是比较喜欢钉钉，实时，信息阅览性强，以下是在实际工作中使用的配置，希望对大家有帮助.</h3>\r\n1.打开钉钉windows 客户端，点击头像下拉菜单--&gt;机器人管理--&gt;点击自定义\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-327\" src=\"http://www.yunfuzg.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/dingding1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"676\" height=\"545\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-332\" src=\"http://www.yunfuzg.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/dingding3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"676\" height=\"545\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-333\" src=\"http://www.yunfuzg.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/dingding4.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"676\" height=\"545\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n2.获取钉钉机器人的webhook，点击机器人的管理按钮--&gt;webhook一栏就是需要的信息\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-337\" src=\"http://www.yunfuzg.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/dingding5.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"676\" height=\"545\" />\r\n\r\n3.在zabbix服务端，修改zabbix_server.conf文件中的AlertScriptsPath=/usr/lib/zabbix/alertscripts（把路径指向脚本存放的路径）\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">4.在/usr/lib/zabbix/alertscripts下新建dingding.py文件，文件内容如下：</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>#!/usr/bin/python\r\n# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-\r\n# Author: xxxxxxxx\r\nimport requests\r\nimport json\r\nimport sys\r\nimport os\r\nheaders = {\'Content-Type\': \'application/json;charset=utf-8\'}\r\napi_url = \"https://oapi.dingtalk.com/robot/send?\r\naccess_token=88da9ed421bf34a2e0c0cbed6a0f60cd2660d1efb547028f13257b4a5519bb25\"\r\ndef msg(text):\r\n    json_text= {\r\n     \"msgtype\": \"text\",\r\n        \"at\": {\r\n            \"atMobiles\": [\r\n                \"zabbix\"\r\n            ],\r\n            \"isAtAll\": False\r\n        },\r\n        \"text\": {\r\n            \"content\": text\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n    print requests.post(api_url,json.dumps(json_text),headers=headers).content\r\nif __name__ == \'__main__\':\r\n    text = sys.argv[1]\r\n    msg(text)</pre>\r\n5.将执行权限授给dingding.py,并测试脚本是否正常运行\r\n<p