 width=\"741\" height=\"920\" />\r\n\r\n触发器恢复后通知信息\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-349\" src=\"http://www.yunfuzg.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/zabbix9.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"772\" height=\"785\" />\r\n\r\n10.至此当服务器发生故障，我们在钉钉群能查看到哪台主机出现故障，帮忙运维人员快速定位故障。', 'zabbix实战应用-zabbix配置钉钉报警', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '246-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-12-13 18:08:21', '2018-12-13 10:08:21', '', '246', 'http://www.yunfuzg.com/246-revision-v1/373.html', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
