INSERT INTO k8s_posts VALUES ('511', '1', '2018-12-15 12:21:37', '2018-12-15 04:21:37', '<h3>zabbix众多的报警接收工具中，个人还是比较喜欢钉钉，实时，信息阅览性强，以下是在实际工作中使用的配置，希望对大家有帮助.</h3>\r\n<h6>1.打开钉钉windows客户端，点击头像下拉菜单--&gt;机器人管理--&gt;点击自定义</h6>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-327\" src=\"http://www.yunfuzg.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/dingding1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"676\" height=\"545\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-332\" src=\"http://www.yunfuzg.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/dingding3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"676\" height=\"545\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-333\" src=\"http://www.yunfuzg.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/dingding4.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"676\" height=\"545\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h6>2.获取钉钉机器人的webhook，点击机器人的管理按钮--&gt;webhook一栏就是需要的信息</h6>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-337\" src=\"http://www.yunfuzg.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/dingding5.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"676\" height=\"545\" />\r\n<h6>3.在zabbix服务端，修改zabbix_server.conf文件中的AlertScriptsPath=/usr/lib/zabbix/alertscripts（把路径指向脚本存放的路径）</h6>\r\n<h6 style=\"text-align: left;\">4.在/usr/lib/zabbix/alertscripts下新建dingding.py文件，文件内容如下：</h6>\r\n[cce]\r\n#!/usr/bin/python\r\n# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-\r\n# Author: xxxxxxxx\r\nimport requests\r\nimport json\r\nimport sys\r\nimport os\r\nheaders = {\'Content-Type\': \'application/json;charset=utf-8\'}\r\napi_url = \"修改成你的钉钉webhook\"\r\ndef msg(text):\r\njson_text= {\r\n\"msgtype\": \"text\",\r\n\"at\": {\r\n\"atMobiles\": [\r\n\"zabbix\"\r\n],\r\n\"isAtAll\": False\r\n},\r\n\"text\": {\r\n\"content\": text\r\n}\r\n}\r\nprint requests.post(api_url,json.dumps(json_text),headers=headers).content\r\nif __name__ == \'__main__\':\r\ntext = sys.argv[1]\r\nmsg(text)\r\n[/cce]\r\n<h6>5.将执行权限授给dingding.py,并测试脚本是否正常运行</h6>\r\n[cce]\r\n[root@localhost alertscripts]# chmod +x dingding.py\r\n[root@localhost alertscripts]# python dingding.py 123\r\n{\"errmsg\":\"ok\",\"errcode\":0}\r\n[/cce]\r\n<h6>6.如出现以上信息和钉钉接受到信息表示脚本运行成功，可以进行下一步操作</h6>\r\n<h6>7.使用web浏览器登陆zabbix，选择管理--&gt;报警媒介类型--&gt;点击创建媒体类型--&gt;根据以下信息填写--&gt;点击更新提交</h6>\r\n<h6><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-358\" src=\"http://www.yunfuzg.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/zabbix11.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1069\" height=\"150\" /></h6>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-357\" src=\"http://www.yunfuzg.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/zabbix12.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1057\" height=\"454\" />\r\n<h6>8.点击zabbix web端用户配置报警媒介</h6>\r\n点击管理--&gt;用户--&gt;点击你所使用的用户（我用的是默认管理员账号）\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-352\" src=\"http://www.yunfuzg.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/zabbix15.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1055\" height=\"316\" />\r\n\r\n进入用户界面后点击报警媒介--&gt;添加\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-355\" src=\"http://www.yunfuzg.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/zabbix14.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1058\" height=\"274\" />\r\n\r\n根据之前创建脚本填写信息--&gt;点击更新\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-343\" src=\"http://www.yunfuzg.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/zabbix3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1022\" height=\"394\" />\r\n\r\n最后一步点击更新保存配置\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-353\" src=\"http://www.yunfuzg.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/zabbix16.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1053\" height=\"295\" />\r\n<h6>9.配置动作，将报警信息通过钉钉发送到钉钉群上</h6>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-358\" src=\"http://www.yunfuzg.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/zabbix11.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1069\" height=\"150\" />\r\n\r\n填写需要的信息并点击操作\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-351\" src=\"http://www.yunfuzg.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/zabbix7.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"790\" height=\"438\" />\r\n\r\n一下是报警触发时发出的信息\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-350\" src=\"http://www.yunfuzg.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/zabbix8.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"741\" height=\"920\" />\r\n\r\n触发器恢复后通知信息\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-349\" src=\"http://www.yunfuzg.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/zabbix9.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"772\" height=\"785\" />\r\n<h6>10.至此当服务器发生故障，我们在钉钉群能查看到哪台主机出现故障，帮忙运维人员快速定位故障。</h6>', 'zabbix实战应用-zabbix配置钉钉报警', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '246-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-12-15 12:21:37', '2018-12-15 04:21:37', '', '246', 'https://www.yunfuzg.com/246-revision-v1/511.html', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO k8s_posts VALUES ('515', '1', '2018-12-15 14:45:06', '2018-12-15 06:45:06', '<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-497\" src=\"https://www.yunfuzg.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/tengxuyun.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"271\" />\r\n\r\n公司很多业务都部署在腾讯云上，大部分都是使用VPC网络，需要通过VPN连接才能进行管理\r\n<h3>PPTP安装</h3>\r\n查看系统环境：\r\n<pre>[cce]\r\n[root@k8sz wwwlogs]# uname -r\r\n3.10.0-693.2.2.el7.x86_64\r\n[root@k8sz wwwlogs]# \r\n[/cce]</pre>\r\n<h2 id=\"h2-u5B89u88C5\">安装</h2>\r\n直接使用yum安装\r\n<pre>[cce][root@master ~]# yum install ppp pptpd[/cce]</pre>\r\n<h2 id=\"h2--pptp\">配置pptp</h2>\r\n<pre>[cce]\r\n[root@master ~]# vi /etc/pptpd.conf\r\nlocalip 172.10.26.1\r\nremoteip 172.10.26.128-245\r\n[/cce]</pre>\r\n<h2 id=\"h2--pptp-\">配置pptp用户</h2>\r\n<pre>[cce]\r\n[root@master ~]# vim /etc/ppp/chap-secrets \r\n格式：\r\n    client(用户名)        server(服务)  secret(密码)                  IP addresses(登录获取的ip)\r\nLorne   pptpd Lorne*&amp;31026 172.10.26.128\r\n[/cce]</pre>\r\n<h2 id=\"h2-u5F00u542Fu5185u6838u8F6Cu53D1\">开启内核转发</h2>\r\n<pre>[cce]\r\n[root@master ~]# echo \'net.ipv4.ip_forward = 1\' &gt;&gt; /etc/sysctl.conf \r\n[root@master ~]# sysctl -p\r\n[/cce]</pre>\r\n<h2 id=\"h2--iptables-\">配置iptables转发规则</h2>\r\n<pre>[cce]\r\n[root@master system]# systemctl stop firewalld.service\r\n[root@master system]# systemctl disable firewalld.service\r\n[root@master system]# yum install iptables-services \r\n[root@master ~]# iptables -t nat -A POSTROUTING -s 172.10.26.0/24 -j SNAT --to-source 192.168.1.225\r\n[root@master ~]# iptables -A FORWARD -p tcp --syn -s 172.10.26.0/24 -j TCPMSS --set-mss 1356  将mtu包改小些，防止pptp mtu过大导致其他网络服务堵塞\r\n[root@master system]# systemctl restart iptables.service\r\n[root@master system]# systemctl enable iptables.service\r\n[/cce]</pre>\r\n<h2 id=\"h2--dns\">添加DNS</h2>\r\n<pre>[cce]\r\n# vim /etc/ppp/options.pptpd\r\nms-dns 223.5.5.5\r\nms-dns 223.6.6.6\r\n[/cce]</pre>\r\n<h2 id=\"h2--pptpd\">需要上外网iptables设置</h2>\r\n<pre>[cce]\r\niptables -t nat -A POSTROUTING -s 172.16.88.0/24 -o eth0 -j MASQUERADE\r\n\r\niptables -A INPUT -p tcp --dport 1723 -j ACCEPT\r\n\r\niptables -I FORWARD -p tcp --syn -i ppp+ -j TCPMSS --set-mss 1300   （关键）\r\n\r\niptables -A POSTROUTING -t nat -s 172.16.88.0/24 -j SNAT --to 172.16.0.15\r\n[/cce]</pre>\r\n<h2 id=\"h2--pptpd\">启动pptpd</h2>\r\n<pre>[cce]\r\n[root@master system]# systemctl start pptpd\r\n[root@master system]# systemctl enable pptpd\r\n[/cce]</pre>\r\n<h2 id=\"h2-u5BA2u6237u7AEFu8FDEu63A5\">客户端连接</h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-499\" src=\"https://www.yunfuzg.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/vpn.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"495\" height=\"764\" />', '腾讯云主机centos7搭建PPTP server', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '498-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-12-15 14:45:06', '2018-12-15 06:45:06', '', '498', 'https://www.yunfuzg.com/498-revision-v1/515.html', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
