INSERT INTO k8s_posts VALUES ('595', '1', '2019-01-10 11:16:18', '2019-01-10 03:16:18', '<img class=\"size-medium wp-image-597 aligncenter\" src=\"https://www.yunfuzg.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/lvm-300x169.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"169\" />\r\n\r\n阿里云服务器确定好购买的云盘添加挂载到ECS主机，或者对现有云盘进行扩容（阿里云盘最大支持2000G）\r\n\r\n1.查看云盘是否挂载成功\r\n<pre>[cce]\r\n# ls /dev/xvd*\r\n/dev/xvda   /dev/xvdb   /dev/xvdb2  /dev/xvdc  /dev/xvdd1  /dev/xvde1  /dev/xvdf1  /dev/xvdg1  /dev/xvdh1  /dev/xvdi1\r\n/dev/xvda1  /dev/xvdb1  /dev/xvdb3  /dev/xvdd  /dev/xvde   /dev/xvdf   /dev/xvdg   /dev/xvdh   /dev/xvdi   /dev/xvdj\r\n#其中/dev/xvdj是我新挂载的云盘\r\n[/cce]</pre>\r\n2.进行云盘分区\r\n<pre>[cce]\r\n# fdisk /dev/xvdj\r\nCommand (m for help): p     #查看云盘信息\r\nDisk /dev/xvdj: 1099.5 GB, 1099511627776 bytes\r\n255 heads, 63 sectors/track, 133674 cylinders\r\nUnits = cylinders of 16065 * 512 = 8225280 bytes\r\nSector size (logical/physical): 512 bytes / 512 bytes\r\nI/O size (minimum/optimal): 512 bytes / 512 bytes\r\nDisk identifier: 0x8ac3108\r\nCommand (m for help): n     #进行分区操作\r\nCommand action\r\n   e   extended\r\n   p   primary partition (1-4)\r\np                           #分别输入P，回车,1，回车，回车，回车\r\nPartition number (1-4): 1   \r\nFirst cylinder (1-133674, default 1): \r\nUsing default value 1\r\nLast cylinder, +cylinders or +size{K,M,G} (1-133674, default 133674): \r\nUsing default value 133674\r\nCommand (m for help): t     #进行磁盘标识划分，分别输入t,回车,8e,回车\r\nSelected partition 1\r\nHex code (type L to list codes): 8e   #注意LVM的标识是8e \r\nChanged system type of partition 1 to 8e (Linux LVM)\r\nCommand (m for help): w    #输入w，回车进行信息保存\r\nThe partition table has been altered!\r\n\r\nCalling ioctl() to re-read partition table.\r\nSyncing disks.\r\n[/cce]</pre>\r\n3.查看分区信息\r\n<pre>[cce]\r\n# fdisk -l /dev/xvdj    #查看分区信息\r\n\r\nDisk /dev/xvdj: 1099.5 GB, 1099511627776 bytes\r\n255 heads, 63 sectors/track, 133674 cylinders\r\nUnits = cylinders of 16065 * 512 = 8225280 bytes\r\nSector size (logical/physical): 512 bytes / 512 bytes\r\nI/O size (minimum/optimal): 512 bytes / 512 bytes\r\nDisk identifier: 0x8ac31082\r\n\r\n    Device Boot      Start         End      Blocks   Id  System\r\n/dev/xvdj1               1      133674  1073736373+  8e  Linux LVM\r\n[/cce]</pre>\r\n4.创建LVM物理卷\r\n<pre>[cce]\r\n# pvcreate /dev/xvdj1\r\n  Physical volume \"/dev/xvdj1\" successfully created\r\n#vgs             #查看卷组\r\n  VG       #PV #LV #SN Attr   VSize VFree\r\n  vgs_data   9   1   0 wz--n- 6.44t 4.95g\r\n[/cce]</pre>\r\n5.加入LVM卷组\r\n<pre>[cce]\r\n# vgextend vgs_data /dev/xvdj1\r\n  Volume group \"vgs_data\" successfully extended\r\n# vgdisplay       #查看\r\n  --- Volume group ---\r\n  VG Name               vgs_data\r\n  System ID             \r\n  Format                lvm2\r\n  Metadata Areas        10\r\n  Metadata Sequence No  21\r\n  VG Access             read/write\r\n  VG Status             resizable\r\n  MAX LV                0\r\n  Cur LV                1\r\n  Open LV               1\r\n  Max PV                0\r\n  Cur PV                10\r\n  Act PV                10\r\n  VG Size               7.44 TiB\r\n  PE Size               4.00 MiB\r\n  Total PE              1950188\r\n  Alloc PE / Size       1686778 / 6.43 TiB\r\n  Free  PE / Size       263410 / 1.00 TiB\r\n  VG UUID               fzxq0F-0IGA-PlsY-GLhI-omKM-3d9x-74ZCac\r\n注意：这里显示剩余的容量还有1TB。所以只能填加1TB.\r\n[/cce]</pre>\r\n6.添加LVM逻辑卷\r\n<pre>[cce]\r\nlvextend -L +1T /dev/vgs_data/lvol0 \r\n  Size of logical volume vgs_data/lvol0 changed from 6.43 TiB (1686778 extents) to 7.43 TiB (1948922 extents).\r\n  Logical volume lvol0 successfully resized.\r\n[/cce]</pre>\r\n7.同步文件系统\r\n<pre>[cce]\r\n# resize2fs /dev/vgs_data/lvol0\r\nresize2fs 1.41.12 (17-May-2010)\r\nFilesystem at /dev/vgs_data/lvol0 is mounted on /opt; on-line resizing required\r\nold desc_blocks = 412, new_desc_blocks = 476\r\nPerforming an on-line resize of /dev/vgs_data/lvol0 to 1995696128 (4k) blocks.\r\nThe filesystem on /dev/vgs_data/lvol0 is now 1995696128 blocks long.\r\n#根据LVM的大小，这个阶段会持续一段时间,这里我花了30多分钟才完成\r\n[/cce]</pre>\r\n8.如果是直接扩容云盘，可直接进行6，7步骤\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'LVM扩容', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'lvm%e6%89%a9%e5%ae%b9', '', '', '2019-03-04 11:25:22', '2019-03-04 03:25:22', '', '0', 'https://www.yunfuzg.com/?p=595', '0', 'post', '', '0');
